### Demo Rate Limiting - Test nhanh

### Bước 1: Lấy JWT Token
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json
ClientId: demo-client

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### Bước 2: Test Rate Limiting cho Pricing GET (5/giây)
### Chạy 6 requests liên tiếp - request thứ 6 sẽ bị rate limited

### Request 1
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-pricing

### Request 2  
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-pricing

### Request 3
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-pricing

### Request 4
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-pricing

### Request 5
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-pricing

### Request 6 - SẼ BỊ RATE LIMITED (429)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-pricing

